fields.description:
This is our first Titanium app to be deployed in the MobileIron app store.

We sign and try to deploy iOS IPA and Android APK files. The apps work in our Beta store but they do not show up in the MobileIron app store. 

Version 1.0 did show for some people but not all people and subsequent releases, 1.0.1, 1.0.2, 1.0.3, and 1.0.4 do not show up at all.
fields.summary: App does not show up in Mobile Iron
